name: Organic Positively Botanicals Company, Catnip Herbal Tea Loose Leaf, Botanical, 4 Ounce
product_description: Catnip, or Nepeta cataria, isn’t just a fun plant for your pet cat. In fact, catnip provides a calming and soothing effect on humans. Catnip is a member of the mint family and is a popular herb used both alone as a tea or tincture or added to relaxing herbal blends. The perennial has a square stem, grayish-green leaves and fragrant pink flowers. Catnip is native to the Mediterranean, Asia and Africa. It was introduced to North America by European settlers and can now be found in many gardens across the United States.
